    net.minecraftforge.common.extensions.IForgeContainerType<T>, net.minecraftforge.registries.IForgeRegistryEntry<net.minecraft.inventory.container.ContainerType<?>>

    public class ContainerTypeData<T extends net.minecraft.inventory.container.Container>
extends net.minecraft.inventory.container.ContainerType<T>
    A ContainerType for a IContainerFactory, which enables additional information to be passed to containers using packet buffers. This enables more convenient syntax via lambdas than the default ContainerType. For example: `new ContainerTypeData(ContainerAbilityContainer::new))`.
